    metaTitle: "Top 100 Addictions Counsellor Exam Questions (2025) | NurseNest",
    metaDescription: "Practice 100 essential IC&RC and CCAC addictions counselling exam questions. Covers motivational interviewing, withdrawal management, harm reduction, ethics, and treatment planning.",
    keywords: "addictions counsellor exam questions, IC&RC exam prep, CCAC exam questions, substance abuse counselor test, addiction counselling exam, CASAC exam prep, addiction exam practice",
